  "title": "Kiosk Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>Responsible for preparing and serving food and drinks, handling payments, and keeping the kiosk clean and well stocked to ensure a smooth and pleasant customer experience.<a href=\"https://www.jobed.ai/food-kiosk-operator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a>​</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Daily opening to prepare BBQ items, ingredients, according to standard recipes and portion sizes (e.g. deep-frying, grilling meat items).<a href=\"https://goodjobs.com.sg/job-detail/kiosk-attendant-service-kitchen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a>​</p></li><li><p>Greet customers, take orders accurately, and provide basic product recommendations appropriately. <a href=\"https://www.jobed.ai/food-kiosk-operator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a>​</p></li><li><p>Collect payment via cash, cards, or QR/digital methods using a point-of-sale system, issue receipts, and handle cash responsibly.<br /><br />Pack cooked food items, before handing over to customers<br /><br />Daily closing and cleaning up all utensils and kiosk.<br /><a href=\"https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/food-kiosk-assistant-ho-kee-pau-b900ea583bbb312ed78b6f84808acd0e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a>​</p></li></ul>",
